President Trump restarted the White House #covid briefings. He urged Americans to wear masks. He even scrapped his party’s convention.

text:
Almost 100 days ago, Gov. Newsom tapped Apple’s Tim Cook, Disney’s Bob Iger, former Federal Reserve Chair Janet Yellen and scores of other business and labor luminaries to chart the state’s economic recovery.

The public is still waiting for a road map https://t.co/YqWgz9DRTU
